data.description: OPEN HOUSE Saturday, Oct 7 1-4 pm***Better than Brand New 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home!  Meritage is known for energy efficiency and this one was Built only 1 yr ago w/ Open Floor Plan and Tall ceilings. Seller has put in some upgrades you are sure to LOVE! Enter through a beautiful 8' front door with Private Office on the right and lovely kitchen down the hall which has gas cooking, stainless energy-efficient appliances, white cabinets, and light solid countertops. Large family room looks out to covered patio and backyard. Primary Bedroom downstairs w/ Bay Windows facing out to fenced backyard. Luxurious Spa-like Primary Bath to relax. Upstairs is expansive Bonus Room AND a closed in Media Room, along with 3 bedrooms and full bath. Backyard has covered patio for outdoor dining and privacy fence. Great Northside Schools and convenient to lots of shopping and medical facilities.
